This app uses API of "Open Weather Map" to gather information about current weather in 3 cities in Russia:
1. Kazan
2. Moscow
3. Saint-Petersburg

Prerequisites:
JDK 1.8 or higher
TomCat 7

The best way to run this app is to import it to Intellij Idea and build it using custom "Mvn deploy" build.
Then typo into your browser localhost:<port configured for tomcat server>/WeatherApp

For example:
localhost:8080/WeatherApp

Any questions regarding this project you can address to philippsbucket@gmail.com
